-- Eni Plans to Reschedule Gulf of Mexico Projects Following BP Crude Spill
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-07-28T10:36:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/eni-plans-to-reschedule-gulf-of-mexico-projects-following-bp-crude-spill.html

          
          
             Eni SpA, Italy’s largest oil and gas
company, said it expects to reschedule “certain projects” in
the Gulf of Mexico as a consequence of BP Plc’s oil spill,
according to a statement distributed by the Italian exchange.  
          
          


  


        